e forecast is good we head out there. I love being on the coast and its good to have a chill off the bike every now and then.\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<em>Gotta ask, What was going through your head just before you did the backflip over the canyon at the 2013 Red Bull Rampage? Did you plan it, or did it it just sort of come up in the moment?</em>\r\n\r\nHahah I have had that question a few times... Yeah I did plan it, I thought about it for a while... I was mostly reminding myself to \"spin slow,spin slow\" it was such a big jump I knew I didn\'t need to pull back much at all, it was awesome feeling I want to do it again!\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<em>What does the expression Live Out mean to you?</em>\r\n\r\nGet outside and live your dream!\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<em>Would you consider using Live Out to find new trails when you come to the U.S.?</em>\r\n\r\nYeah for sure, it\'s sometimes hard when you are traveling to find places to shred and people to shred them with, Live Out is a good way to get in touch with people that want to do the same stuff as you do.\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\nConnect with Kelly!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nInterview by Scott McGuire\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.liveout.org/\">http://www.liveout.org</a>\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\nAbout\r\n\r\nLive Out is a new web-app &amp; social network where you can find people with outdoor interests, discover the best places to go &amp; find fun things to do outdoors near you.','Catching Up With Pro Mountain Biker Kelly McGarry','','inherit','open','open','','30-revision-v1','','','2015-02-20 01:42:34','2015-02-20 01:42:34','',30,'http://localhost/blog/30-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(37,1,'2015-02-20 01:43:15','2015-02-20 01:43:15','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe recently had the chance to catch up with professional mountain biker &amp; GoPro athlete Kelly McGarry. You may remember Kelly from last 