ou come to the U.S.?</em>\r\n\r\nYeah for sure, it\'s sometimes hard when you are traveling to find places to shred and people to shred them with, Live Out is a good way to get in touch with people that want to do the same stuff as you do.\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\nConnect with Kelly!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kellymcgarrymtb?fref=nf\">https://www.facebook.com/kellymcgarrymtb?fref=nf</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/kellymcgazza\">https://twitter.com/kellymcgazza</a>\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/kellymcgazza/\">https://instagram.com/kellymcgazza/</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nInterview by Scott McGuire\r\n\r\nWriter for <a href=\"http://www.liveout.org\">Live Out: The Outdoor Social Network</a>\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>About Live Out</strong>\r\n\r\nLive Out is a new web-app &amp; social network where you can find people with outdoor interests, discover the best places to go &amp; find fun things to do outdoors near you.','Catching Up With Professional Mountain Biker Kelly McGarry','','inherit','open','open','','30-revision-v1','','','2015-02-20 02:41:36','2015-02-20 02:41:36','',30,'http://localhost/blog/30-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(51,1,'2015-02-20 02:45:32','2015-02-20 02:45:32','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe recently had the chance to catch up with professional mountain biker &amp; GoPro athlete Kelly McGarry. You may remember Kelly from last years Red Bull Rampage as the guy who busted out a back-flip over the 72-ft canyon during the middle of his silver medal run. In case you missed it, check out this rad video:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x76VEPXYaI0\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSo we sat down Kelly to hear about his plans, goals, and passion for mountain biking...\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>What motivates you to ride &amp; what do you enjoy most about it?</em>\r\n\r\nI guess one of the main things I enjoy about riding is sessioning with my mates, its always fun an