is year.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>\"I\'m playing in the Masters,\" Tiger said Friday afternoon. \"It\'s obviously very important to me, and I want to be there.”</em>\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\nAfter backing out of the Honda Classic and the Arnold Palmer Invitational - two of his regular warm-ups for the Masters, there has been a lot of speculation as to whether or not Tiger will play at Augusta this year. The first real evidence that he would did not come until just earlier this week when his plane was spotted at the Augusta airport.\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\nThis will be Tigers first appearance on Tour in over two months. In his last showing, he withdrew from the Farmers Insurance Open in the middle of the round due to back stiffness.\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\nHere’s the real question: <em>Will Tiger be Tiger?</em>\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\nIt’s been <b>10 years</b> since his last Masters win. He missed the tournament altogether for the first time last year due to back surgery. It’s also been <b>19 months</b> since his last major win. Wood’s last “Tiger-like” year was 2013, when he finished with five (5) titles. But 2014 proved perhaps his worst year yet, with not one top-10 finish in nine starts. Needless to say, he’s been a little rusty lately. Following his struggles, Woods made a statement that he would not return until he felt he could compete with the best players in the world.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nGoing into the 2015 Masters, it will be the first time Woods has been ranked out of the top 100 (104) since his first year on tour. All speculation aside, Tiger remains focused and optimistic:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<em>\"I\'ve worked a lot on my game and I\'m looking forward to competing. I\'m excited to get to Augusta and I appreciate everyone\'s support.\"</em>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWhile the question remains whether he’s got his edge back, one thing\'s for certain - golf is always more fun to watch when Tiger is in the hunt.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n#GetReady\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_L1P1TmuOoU\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Scott-McGuire_Live-Out_The-Outdoor-Social-Network.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-600\" src=\"http://localhost/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Scott-McGuire_Live-Out_The-Outdoor-Social-Network.jpg\" alt=\"Scott McGuire\" width=\"180\" height=\"180\" /></a>\r\n\r\nAuthor: Scott McGuire\r\n\r\n<strong><strong> </strong></strong>\r\n\r\nLeave a comment!','Tiger Woods Announces He Will Play in the 2015 Masters','','publish','open','open','','tiger-woods-announces-he-will-play-in-the-2015-masters','','','2015-04-03 21:02:49','2015-04-03 21:02:49','',0,'http://localhost/blog/?p=592',0,'post','',0),(593,1,'2015-04-03 20:32:58','2015-04-03 20:32:58','Masters at Augusta','Tiger Woods_Masters at Augusta','','inherit','open','open','','tiger-woods_masters-at-augusta','','','2015-04-03 20:33:22','2015-04-03 20:33:22','',592,'http://localhost/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Tiger-Woods_Masters-at-Augusta.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(594,1,'2015-04-03 20:37:56','2015-04-03 20:37:56','UA Boxerjock Cycling Apparel','Under Armour','','inherit','open','open','','under-armour-2','','','2015-04-07 22:10:59','2015-04-07 22:10:59','',592,'http://localhost/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/Under-Armour.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(595,1,'2015-04-03 20:40:04','2015-04-03 20:40:04','','TaylorMade Golf','','inherit','open','open','','taylormade-golf','','','2015-04-03 20:40:04','2015-04-03 20:40:04','',592,'http://localhost/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/TaylorMade-Golf.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(596,1,'2015-04-03 20:42:09','2015-04-03 20:42:09','#1 Driver in Golf','TaylorMade Golf','','inherit','open','open','','taylormade-golf-2','','','2015-04-03 20:42:41','2015-04-03 20:42:41','',592,'http://localhost/blog/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/